  All complex types now implement Debug trait:
  - InfrawareTerminal (Debug)
  - InfrawareTerminalBuilder (Debug)
  - CompiledPatterns (Debug)
  - CommandCache (Debug)
  - ClassifierChain (Debug)
  - KnownCommandHandler (Debug)
  - InputClassifier (Debug)
  - TerminalUI (Debug)
  - HttpLLMClient (Debug)
end note

@enduml
